<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#89435aa608b148b48a4c4f7:FPSpecific">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#FPSpecific"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">89435aa608b148b48a4c4f7</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">What is the effective date of this Policy and when does this policy apply? This Policy is effective as of the date set out above We reserve the right to modify this Policy at any time and such revisions will become effective upon the earlier of a posting of the revisions to the Sites or b distribution by electronic mail Your continued use of any of the Sites or the Services after the effective date of the revisions means that you accept and agree to any such revisions This Policy applies solely to our on-line information gathering and disclosure practices in connection with the Sites and does not apply to any of our practices conducted off-line</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

