  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">If you no longer wish to receive our announcements by e-mail you may unsubscribe from receiving them at any time by choosing the Unsubscribe link at the bottom of our e-mails or by writing to us at privacy taylorswift com If you e-mail us to change your contact preferences we will implement your requested changes within a reasonable period of time Please note that your requested changes will not be effective until we implement such changes Please also note that you cannot unsubscribe from certain correspondence from us such as messages relating to your account transactions</evidence>
